summary: After finishing my BA Archaeology (specailized in Middle Eastern Archaeology) at Leiden University, I moved to Jordan to study the Archaeology of Petra (Jordan) and the rich Jordanian history and culture. With my efforts, I am hoping to raise awareness about the ongoing deterioration in the Petra Archaeological Park and thereby trying to enhance efforts and prevent loss of important data. Likewise having a major interest in all other Archaeological sites in Jordan. Currently back in the Netherlands, hoping to contribute to Archaeological research in either the Netherlands and / or Middle East.
